NAME
       cd - change the current directory

SYNOPSIS
       cd [PATH]

DESCRIPTION
       Change the working directory to PATH.

       Use '..' to go up one level, and '/' or '~' to return to
       the root. PATH may be nested, e.g. 'cd projects'.

SEE ALSO
       ls(1), pwd(1), cat(1), man(1)

